{"tid":2329294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莊正被控暴動罪過堂：心很累 案件預計2022年年中開審","createTime":"2020-12-17T06:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T17:38:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":295,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"d13db0e38ff7fb5b4f86f28bd2968ad6808d6cff","tid":2329294,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"去年由200萬民眾上街開始，社會運動大受關注，連藝人也上街表態抗爭，可惜在重重打壓下遭濫捕，分分鐘官非纏身，為公義付出代價。2019年Sony旗下樂壇男新人莊正（Lester），去年在理大圍城時身處現場被警方拘捕，及後被控告暴動罪。日前他在fb留言：「朝早9點半上庭過堂，傾過話有機會排到2022年年中先審，心很累，但我OK。」莊正為了抗爭犧牲事業，被捕後他於社交平台向歌迷交代，表示主動與唱片公司在今年1月解約，之後以獨立歌手的身份，推出過歌曲《Will (not) see you soon.》，透過歌詞大談社會事件下人們的恐懼與不安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/U5AHFLF3XFFHNBULSLCHFS626E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2FU5AHFLF3XFFHNBULSLCHFS626E%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28SZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=cc4416c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2FU5AHFLF3XFFHNBULSLCHFS626E%2F&h=31e10746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/U5AHFLF3XFFHNBULSLCHFS626E/</a>"},{"pid":"bb8e2bb5bdf3026666e638daa4f231a552691426","tid":2329294,"uid":41368,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"21定22？<br />\n咁耐？"},{"pid":"392bed1c821759d021d8d7caf1c24e7c5df46f85","tid":2329294,"uid":271513,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"搞咁耐先審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2be165dca111d28b91976922364b7ba8926dc1d","tid":2329294,"uid":43062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<